org.apache.flink.runtime.managementgraph

Class ManagementGroupEdge

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.managementgraph.ManagementAttachment
      • org.apache.flink.runtime.managementgraph.ManagementGroupEdge

  • public final class ManagementGroupEdge
extends ManagementAttachment
    This class implements a directed edge of between two ManagementGroupVertex objects. The edge is derived from a group edge of the actual execution graph.

    This class is not thread-safe.
